long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Solves the problem of skeets being called posts on Bluesky by changing "Post" to "Skeet", "repost" to "reskeet", "quote post" to "quote skeet", and "reposted" to "reskeeted".
